{
  "stem": "8610.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we knew that if you go over there, that's the end.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there's no survivors, if you've-- once you've-- where Mengele and, and his-- has his 'selections,' as they called them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was faced with this problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Can I officiate at this wedding?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got in touch with my religious authorities in London.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I told them the situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And their answer was categorically no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Until such time as we have a complete list of survivors, you can't because it might-- they might-- their partners might turn up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I thought this was an absurdity beyond words.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How long are we going to wait till they get a complete list of survivors?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It'll take years.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They're traveling all over the place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "God knows where they are.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had one case in particular.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A man comes to me, shows me a piece of paper on which it says, I so-and-so, the son of so-and-so, take so-and-so's-- the daughter of so-and-so as my wife, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] witnessed by-- and there were two people signed as witnesses.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said to them, mazel tov, you're married.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Common law, if you like, but you're married.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People began to live together as husband and wife.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You couldn't stop them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I looked the other way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What else am I going to do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a human issue.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People in London didn't appreciate the situation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, you-- it's impossible to visualize it or imagine it until you've seen it on the spot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and power of words isn't enough to describe this sort of situation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And these people were beginning to, to feel that they are human again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it's a wonderful thing to think that they have-- what they've been through, that they're no longer skeletons.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
